sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/Scheduler
    participant A02 as Agent 02\nNewsletter
    participant A01 as Agent 01\nMarket Data
    participant A03 as Agent 03\nScoring
    participant A08 as Agent 08\nConstructor
    participant A09 as Agent 09\nIncome Metrics
    participant A11 as Agent 11\nHealth
    participant A12 as Agent 12\nProposal
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant UI as User Interface

    note over U,UI: Flow 1 — Portfolio Review (scheduled / user-initiated)
    U->>A09: trigger portfolio review
    A09->>DB: read positions + portfolios
    A09->>DB: write portfolio_income_metrics
    A09->>A11: trigger health score
    A11->>DB: read metrics + constraints
    A11->>DB: write portfolio_health_scores
    A11->>A03: rescore stale positions
    A03->>DB: write income_scores
    A11->>A12: thresholds breached?
    A12->>DB: read all context (Asset × Position × Portfolio)
    A12->>UI: proposals
    UI-->>U: notification

    note over U,UI: Flow 2 — Analyst Signal
    A02->>DB: write analyst_articles + recommendations
    A02->>A03: score ticker
    A03->>DB: read features_historical
    A03->>DB: write income_scores
    A03->>DB: cross-ref portfolios holding ticker
    A03->>A12: actionable signal
    A12->>UI: proposal
    UI-->>U: notification

    note over U,UI: Flow 3 — Circuit Breaker
    A01->>DB: price/data event detected
    A01->>DB: identify positions holding ticker
    A01->>A03: rescore (portfolio weight context)
    A03->>A12: severity-weighted alert
    A12->>UI: alert / proposal
    UI-->>U: notification

    note over U,UI: Flow 4 — Portfolio Construction (Greenfield)
    U->>A08: constraints only, no positions
    A08->>DB: create DRAFT portfolio
    A08->>DB: write PROPOSED positions
    A08->>A12: rank proposals
    A12->>UI: ranked proposal set
    UI-->>U: review
    U->>DB: approve → PROPOSED→ACTIVE, DRAFT→ACTIVE
